## Puppet-Logrotate
## Tom De Vylder
## tomdv (a) penumbra.be
## 2011-03-14

BASIC USAGE:

	node 'node1.domain.tld' {
		logrotate::file { "apache2":
			source     => "/etc/logrotate.d/apache2",
			postrotate => "/etc/init.d/apache2 reload > /dev/null",
			log        => [	"/var/log/apache2/access.log", "/var/log/apache2/error.log" ],
			options    => 
				[ 
					"weekly", 
					"compress", 
					"rotate 52", 
					"missingok"
				]
		}
	}
